overview: Plenty have had an opinion on the colourful football career of Dane Swan.  In fact in 258 games, the 2011 Brownlow Medallist created probably just as many headlines.  It all came to an end in 2016 when Swan suffered a foot injury that would go on to end his famous ride in the Black and White.  And throughout the season, Collingwood Media was there for every step.
tagline: Watch Collingwood capture the story of the 2016 season.
title: Last Call
